WEBVTT

00:03:27.686 --> 00:03:30.000
I'm looking at this warm towel;

00:03:30.024 --> 00:03:33.418
I don't know what to do with my life,
let alone with this damn towel --

00:03:33.442 --> 00:03:35.319
(Laughter)

00:03:35.343 --> 00:03:38.161
(Applause)

00:03:39.712 --> 00:03:41.051
I did one of the --

00:03:41.075 --> 00:03:43.565
you know, anything anyone
could do in that situation:

00:03:44.043 --> 00:03:46.740
look around, see what
everyone else is doing.

00:03:46.764 --> 00:03:47.948
I did the same.

00:03:48.549 --> 00:03:53.586
Mind you, I drove about seven hours
from my village to the airport that day.

00:03:54.524 --> 00:03:56.574
So I grab this warm towel,

00:03:56.598 --> 00:03:59.743
wipe my face just like
everyone else is doing,

00:03:59.767 --> 00:04:01.213
I look at it --